<h2>Watch If You Liked…</h2>
<p>If <em>Disclosure Day</em> left you staring at the ceiling at 2am, go back and watch <em>Arrival</em> — or better yet, <em>Annihilation</em>, which will do the same thing but worse (in the best way). More of a <em>Killer Whale</em> person? <em>Crawl</em> and <em>The Shallows</em> are waiting for you and they don't bite any less hard.</p>

